  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Recent studies have shown beneficial effects of sildenafil in patients with single ventricle
      congenital heart disease. The purpose of this study is to determine whether Bosentan, a drug
      with similar effects, will have similar benefit in this patient population.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients enrolled in the study will take Bosentan. Baseline and follow up measurements will
      be collected then analyzed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
